{"tid":2116622,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部發言人汪文斌: 英方指新疆推行強制絕育完全是一派胡言","createTime":"2020-07-20T09:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T18:51:45.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d2145fbcf14a7894f51610ef38e129b618d767b3","tid":2116622,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T09:25:59.000Z","msg":"在北京，外交部回應英方指中方在新疆推行所謂強制絕育的報道，批評完全是一派胡言。<br />\n<br />\n發言人汪文斌指，英方有關言論完全是造謠污蔑。中方已經反覆闡述在新疆問題的立場，涉疆問題根本不是人權、宗教、民族問題，而是反暴力恐怖主義和反分裂的問題。<br />\n<br />\n汪文斌指出，以英方所謂強制絕育問題為例，事實是40年來新疆地區的維吾爾族人口從555萬增長到了1165萬，約佔自治區總人口46.8%，所謂的強制絕育的報道完全是一派胡言。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538860-20200720.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538860-20200720.htm&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zbccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=86964ff1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538860-20200720.htm&h=31ff601f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538860-20200720.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5637c82784581ed8a57fc8a7497bf48ccff389bf","tid":2116622,"uid":273703,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T09:27:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a144e409d35d582fa55dbf40d50213e1028e1942","tid":2116622,"uid":286897,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T09:28:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ccc445dbe1793f097978a47ee88772ae8286cb3e","tid":2116622,"uid":24788,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T09:31:41.000Z","msg":"d人都入唔到去<br />\n你講咩都得嫁啦"},{"pid":"36f713b5f1d7af73682e5452bf7801231e808fd0","tid":2116622,"uid":346701,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"d2145fbcf14a7894f51610ef38e129b618d767b3","tid":2116622,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T09:25:59.000Z","msg":"在北京，外交部回應英方指中方在新疆推行所謂強制絕育的報道，批評完全是一派胡言。<br />\n<br />\